==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Defender
<hw>De*fend"er</hw> <pr>(d⟦esl⟧*f⟦ecr⟧nd"⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Cf. <er>Fender</er>.]</ety> <def>One who defends; one who
maintains, supports, protects, or vindicates; a champion; an advocate; a
vindicator.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Provinces . . . left without their ancient and puissant
<qex>defenders</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Motley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Defendress</ent>⟦br⟧
